    "The intermediate layers in the transformers have a size of 3072.",
    "Moreover, the model uses GELU as its activation function and dropout rates for both attention probabilities and hidden layers are set to 0.1 5.",
    "Following, we use a fully connected neural network with one hidden layer that takes the [CLS] token final embedding as input and outputs the number of stars S(x).",
    "We optimize both RELEXset-MLM and RELEXset-Predictor using adam (Kingma & Ba, 2015) with early stopping.",
    "Both RecipeNLG and RELEXset are split into train/validation/test sets with a ratio of 80/10/10."
  ],
